{
  "texts": [
    "• The ability of the Transformer model to identify potential cardiac disease was examined in relation to the impacts of various data preprocessing techniques.",
    "Several pre-processing methods were applied to the input data, and their effects on the model's functionality and accuracy were carefully examined.",
    "The goal of this research is to develop a self-attention-based transformer model for assessing CVD risk utilizing the Cleveland dataset.",
    "This dataset contains a variety of medical and non-medical components that can be used to identify whether a patient has cardiac disease.",
    "The dataset comprises both continuous and categorical variables, among other features."
  ]
}